HOLISTIC MEDICINE: Natural and herbal healing traditions

Category: Medical
Base skill: 35% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Healing through natural and traditional means rather than surgery or
high technology: herbal remedies, acupuncture, massage, and other
practices for treating illness and injury. Common among shamans,
tribal healers, monks, and anyone raised outside the Coalition's
Western-style medical system.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

